    "This low uptake may be explained by lack of journal mandates in instructions to authors.",
    "The CONSORT-AI extension was mandated by only two of the 52 journals in which the included studies were published, with one additional journal recommending its use without mandate.",
    "Other journals either recommended CONSORT 2010 or signposted to generic resources like the EQUATOR Network, where finding CONSORT-AI would be up to the individual authors' initiative.",
    "Previous research on instructions for authors in high impact factor journals, in the context of CONSORT 2010, has shown that journal endorsement is sometimes lackingespecially in the endorsement of specific extensions 75.",
